snippet.title: Thief - The Bank Heist DLC Trailer
snippet.description: http://bit.ly/19jLwN3 - As the Master Thief, infiltrate the City's most secure location, Stonemarket First Bank, to steal a coveted family heirloom called the Star of Auldale. To this day, this heavily guarded and treacherous place remains impregnable, but that's about to change...
